latestPosts.caption:
NOW LIVE! Here’s something we made for the hands that do it all 🫧🖐🏽

We could never find a hand wash that didn’t leave our skin feeling dry, tight, or in immediate need of hand cream. So we decided to make our own—because why should our hands bear the brunt of harsh, chemical-laden cleansers?

〰️ It took 23 rounds of tweaking, testing, and starting over to get it right. Making a hand wash sounds simple—but making one that’s 95% naturally derived, non-drying yet truly cleansing, with a soft, comforting lather was harder than you’d think.

We wanted every rinse to feel like a small moment of calm—so we created two uplifting scents:
🍐 Our OG Fresh Reset — uplifting notes of pear, patchouli & rose. 
🍊 Our NEW Mandarin Mist — a bright, energizing blend of geranium and mandarin.

From our hands to yours,
Sejal & Ishaani
the 23rd iteration just worked. stay tuned.
